SUMMARY:Conversations on Grief (virtual)
DESCRIPTION:Conversations on Grief introduces participants to the many dimensions of grief. Explore different aspects of grief and grieving in these educational and supportive online conversations. \nChoose the time/day that best suits your schedule. \nRegistration is required. Call 919-719-7199. \nUnderstanding Grief\nThursday\, March 5 \nAnger\, Guilt\, and Regret\nThursday\, March 12 \nWhy Doesn’t Anyone Understand?\nThursday\, March 19 \nWho Am I Now?\nThursday\, March 26 \nWhere Do I Go From Here?\nThursday\, April 2 \n  \nTransitions GriefCare provides grief support at no charge to the bereaved. If you’d like to help us continue this service\, please consider making a donation at transitionslifecare.org/donate.
URL:https://www.transitionslifecare.org/event/conversations-on-grief-virtual-4/2026-03-19/
LOCATION:Virtual
CATEGORIES:Grief Support,Grief Support for Adults
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.transitionslifecare.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/AdultGrief_L3halfcol.jpg
GEO:35.7595731;-79.0192997
