SUMMARY:KidsZone
DESCRIPTION:A monthly in-person grief group for children ages 5–12 to express grief\, connect with peers\, and enhance coping skills through themed activities. \nSessions alternate monthly between Thursday evenings (with drop-in dinner at 5:30pm) and Saturday afternoons. \nFebruary 19\, March 21\, April 16\, May 16 \nPLEASE NOTE: Please note\, our registration process has changed. If you are interested in a child or teen grief support program or group\, please call 919-719-7199\, email kidsgrief@transitionslifecare.org\, or use the following link to contact us: Contact Us 24/7 – Transitions LifeCare. A grief counselor will connect with you to talk through your child’s needs and determine whether a group is the right fit.
URL:https://www.transitionslifecare.org/event/kidszone-2/2026-03-21/
LOCATION:Transitions LifeCare\, 250 Hospice Circle\, Raleigh\, NC\, 27607\, United States
CATEGORIES:Grief Support,Kids Events
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.transitionslifecare.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/TGC-KidsZone-Graphic.jpg
